Description_lang: Rend damage increased by $s1% and Sudden Death can be triggered by Rend's bleed damage.

description_blz.en_US: Rend damage increased by 30% and Sudden Death can be triggered by Rend's bleed damage.

description_blz.ko_KR: 분쇄의 공격력이 30%만큼 증가합니다. 또한 분쇄의 출혈 피해가 급살을 발동시킵니다.
